==English==

===Intransitive verb===
'''to [[wash]] [[up]]'''

# To [[clean]] the [[utensil]]s, [[dish]]es etc. used in preparing and eating a [[meal]].
#:''If you cook, I'll '''wash up'''''.
# To be [[carry|carried]] on to land by [[water]].
#:''The whale was '''washed up''' on the beach.''

====Synonyms====
*(''clean utensils, dishes, etc.''): [[do the dishes]], [[do the washing-up]]

